    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining, and certain electronic features like the rear power windows are currently non-functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to remain in good working order. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind putting in a little work.",
