      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in truly immaculate condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been subjected to rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such high caliber.",
      "price": 48750.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
