    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept in truly pristine, flawless condition. It honestly looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! If you're looking for that perfect ride without the brand-new price tag, you've found it. Come see it for yourself, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
