    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 in Laguna Seca Blue over Grey Nappa leather. This S54-powered icon features a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a 3.64 limited-slip differential. Mechanical provenance is impeccable: the subframe has been professionally reinforced, rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells, and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul completed utilizing Beisan components. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six exhibits factory-spec compression across all cylinders, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Chassis dynamics are preserved with fresh Bilstein dampers and original-spec bushings. The exterior maintains original paint depth with no UV degradation, while the interior remains showroom-fresh with no pixel loss on the instrument cluster or fatigue on the seat bolsters. A turn-key, investment-quality example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
